QuestData.Title: Za'Tual
QuestData.Description: The Zandalari have been a constant nuisance since we arrived on this island. I've assigned Halduron Brightwing to take charge of dismantling their presence at Za'Tual, in the south.$B$BReport to Halduron when you are best able. He will have work for you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Halduron Brightwing outside of Za'Tual.
